                        </div> 
                        <div class="col-4">
                            <img src="/images/giveaways.png" alt="" width="40" class="img-fluid">
                            <p>Exclusive Giveaways and Discount on travel.</p>
                        </div> 
                        <div class="col-4">
                            <img src="/images/gps-app.png" alt="" width="40" class="img-fluid">
